desc: WAYISO is a direct dropship store. WAYISO has free standard shipping with no minimum purchase and no membership fees. EVER. WAYISO utilizes dropshipping to help reduce product cost and overhead expenses while passing on the savings directly to customers. Free standard shipping is calculated into the retail already.
